data.description: 10+ acres offered in English Chase - Brick Cape Cod  sits on corner lot with front field pond.   Major improvements . 5 bedrooms  4 1 /2 baths with a main level primary bedroom.  Open floor plan with large deck off the  back of house.  Two fireplaces, fully finished basement living suite with separate entrance and garage.  Attic partially finished .  Wood, carpet and tile flooring throughout.   Whole house generator.  Open lot with pond, small  barn and run-in shed,  partially fenced orchard with front field pond.   Horses welcome. Trails open to riders  through out English Chase.   Minutes  from  Interstate 66, Comcast Xfinity  for high speed internet.
